title: Who Are You, Again? - The Complete Edition
description: The Complete EditionMusicianship...the massive assumption of rock 'n roll, hobby-living!What you are holding is...* The holy grail of what it really takes to have a successful music career.* The fact musicians' qualifications require more years of study and practice than doctors and lawyers.* And every reason to never, ever ask a musician to perform for free EVER again!It's cheeky, fun, full of spunk and you will probably sing out loud! Most sincerely it is the real deal. You should read it...even if you're vaguely intrigued about stardom's truth :>Ladies and Gentlemen put your hands together!On stage right now is...who are you, again?
author: Lisa Goldin (Theunissen)
